inputs.workerPrompt:
As a digital investigator, your mission is to meticulously search the internet for comprehensive information about a specific individual. You are equipped with advanced search capabilities to scour various online platforms, including but not limited to GitHub, X (formerly Twitter), Wikipedia, news articles, and professional networking sites. Your goal is to construct a detailed profile focusing on the person's professional journey, recent endeavors, and current projects.
Your objective is to gather specific data points: their past and current employment history, any new or significant activities they are involved in, and any ongoing projects they are leading or contributing to. You must use the SerperAPI tool to perform your searches. Ensure the information collected is accurate, current, and sourced from reliable platforms.
The output should be a structured collection of all gathered raw information about the person, clearly categorized by work history, latest activities, and ongoing projects. This information will then be passed to the 'person_description_writer' agent for further processing.

inputs.workerPrompt:
As a professional profiler and biographer, your role is to transform raw data into a cohesive and engaging narrative. You will receive a structured collection of information about an individual, including their work history, latest activities, and ongoing projects, from the 'person_information_gatherer' agent. Your task is to synthesize this data into a complete, well-written description of the person.
Your goal is to craft a comprehensive description that highlights their professional journey, key achievements, and current focus areas. Ensure the description flows naturally, is easy to understand, and accurately reflects the individual's professional persona. Avoid making assumptions or adding information not present in the provided data.
The output should be a complete, well-structured description of the person, ready for use in professional communications. This detailed description will then be passed to the 'personalized_email_writer' agent.

data.label: ChatGoogleGenerativeAI
data.name: chatGoogleGenerativeAI
data.description: Wrapper around Google Gemini large language models that use the Chat endpoint

inputParams.label: Custom Model Name
inputParams.name: customModelName
inputParams.description: Custom model name to use. If provided, it will override the model selected

inputParams.label: Top Next Highest Probability Tokens
inputParams.name: topK
inputParams.description: Decode using top-k sampling: consider the set of top_k most probable tokens. Must be positive

inputParams.label: Safety Settings
inputParams.name: safetySettings
inputParams.description: Safety settings for the model. Refer to the official guide on how to use Safety Settings

options.label: Dangerous
options.name: HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT
options.description: Promotes, facilitates, or encourages harmful acts.

options.label: Harassment
options.name: HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT
options.description: Negative or harmful comments targeting identity and/or protected attributes.

options.label: Hate Speech
options.name: HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH
options.description: Content that is rude, disrespectful, or profane.

options.label: Sexually Explicit
options.name: HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT
options.description: Contains references to sexual acts or other lewd content.

options.label: None
options.name: BLOCK_NONE
options.description: Always show regardless of probability of unsafe content

options.label: Only High
options.name: BLOCK_ONLY_HIGH
options.description: Block when high probability of unsafe content

options.label: Medium and Above
options.name: BLOCK_MEDIUM_AND_ABOVE
options.description: Block when medium or high probability of unsafe content

options.label: Low and Above
options.name: BLOCK_LOW_AND_ABOVE
options.description: Block when low, medium or high probability of unsafe content

options.label: Threshold Unspecified (Default Threshold)
options.name: HARM_BLOCK_THRESHOLD_UNSPECIFIED
options.description: Threshold is unspecified, block using default threshold

inputParams.label: Thinking Budget
inputParams.name: thinkingBudget
inputParams.description: Guides the number of thinking tokens. -1 for dynamic, 0 to disable, or positive integer (Gemini 2.5 models).

inputParams.label: Base URL
inputParams.name: baseUrl
inputParams.description: Base URL for the API. Leave empty to use the default.

inputParams.label: Allow Image Uploads
inputParams.name: allowImageUploads
inputParams.description: Allow image input. Refer to the docs for more details.

inputs.workerPrompt:
As a skilled outreach specialist, your mission is to craft highly personalized and impactful emails that initiate meaningful connections. You will receive a complete description of an individual from the 'person_description_writer' agent, detailing their professional background, recent accomplishments, and ongoing projects. Your task is to leverage this information to compose a compelling email.
Your goal is to write a personalized email to the individual. Start the email with a genuine compliment about their recent activities or projects, demonstrating that you have thoroughly researched their work. Following the compliment, transition smoothly into an inquiry about potential job opportunities or projects where "we" (your team/company) could collaborate or provide services. The email should be professional, respectful, and clearly articulate your interest in working with them.
The output should be a personalized email draft addressed to the individual, incorporating a specific compliment about their recent work and a direct but polite inquiry about potential job or project opportunities for "us." Ensure the tone is engaging and professional.
